t rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلسَّمَآءِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the sky</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلْأَرْضِۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the earth?</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(There is) no</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَـٰهَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">god</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">but</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هُوَۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَأَنَّىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Then, how</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُؤْفَكُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(are) you deluded?</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>3<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
