 class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And whoever</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَزَكَّىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">purifies himself,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَإِنَّمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then only</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَتَزَكَّىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">he purifies</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِنَفْسِهِۚۦ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for his own self.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِلَى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And to</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمَصِيرُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) the destination.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>18<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
