xt top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَذَابِهَاۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">its torment.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَذَٲلِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Thus</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَجْزِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We recompense</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كُلَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">every</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَفُورٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">ungrateful one.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>36<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
