<p class="ayah 35-41" id="41" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">۞ إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُمْسِكُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">upholds</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٲتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the heavens</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلْأَرْضَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the earth,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">lest</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَزُولَاۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they cease.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَئِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And if</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">زَالَتَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they should cease,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَمْسَكَهُمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">can uphold them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">any</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir