<p class="ayah 35-42" id="42" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَقْسَمُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And they swore</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">by Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَهْدَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) strongest</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَيْمَـٰنِهِمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) their oaths</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَئِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that if</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَآءَهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">came to them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَذِيرٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a warner,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَّيَكُونُنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">surely, they would be</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَهْدَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">more guided</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">than</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِحْدَى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">any</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْأُمَمِۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the nations.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><