ext top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed, He</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَانَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">is</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلِيمًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">All-Knower,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَدِيرًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">All-Powerful.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>44<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
